    dc:title "Phyllodactylus sp. 3 (P. tuberculosus species group, lineage A 11 sensu Blair et al. 2015)" ;
    trt:publishedIn <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/CompCytogen.v14i4.57765> ;
    trt:treatsTaxonName <http://taxon-name.plazi.org/id/Animalia/Phyllodactylus> ;
    a trt:Treatment .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/CompCytogen.v14i4.57765>
    bibo:endPage "638" ;
    bibo:issue "4" ;
    bibo:journal "Comparative Cytogenetics" ;
    bibo:pubDate "2020-12-22" ;
    bibo:startPage "613" ;
    bibo:volume "14" ;
    dc:creator "Castiglia, Riccardo; Flores-Villela, Oscar Alberto; Bezerra, Alexandra M. R.; Gornung, Ekaterina; Annesi, Flavia; Munoz-Alonso, Luis Antonio; Solano, Emanuela" ;
    dc:date "2020" ;
    dc:title "Detection of cryptic diversity in lizards (Squamata) from two Biosphere Reserves in Mesoamerica" ;
    fabio:hasPart <https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/489815>, <https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/489816> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/489815>
    dc:description "Figure 4. TCS network of MT-CYTB haplotypes of Phyllodactylus tuberculosus species group. The colors refer to the 11 lineages reported by Blair et al. (2015) for this species complex. The lineage \" A 11 \" and the new specimens here analysed are indicated (see text for further explanation)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/489815" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/489816>
    dc:description "Figure 5. Karyotypes of A Phyllodactylus sp. 3 (2 n = 38, RCMX 69 male) B Holcosus festivus (2 n = 50, RCMX 224 female) C Holcosus undulatus parvus (2 n = 50, RCMX 77 female) D Aspidoscelis deppii (2 n = 52, RCMX 76 female)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/489816" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

